query:
SELECT id as "id!: i64",
               app_id as "app_id!: i64",
               screenshot as "png: Vec<u8>",
               CAST(strftime('%s', created_at) AS INTEGER) as "created_at_sec!: i64"
        FROM screenshot
        WHERE (?1 IS NULL OR app_id = ?1)
          AND created_at < datetime(?2, 'unixepoch')
        ORDER BY created_at DESC
        LIMIT 1
